Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:42.52,Default,Koharu,0,0,0,,猫鼬 别妨碍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.52,Default,Yukina,0,0,0,,小春 去把剑之介叫起来吧
