Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.12,Default,Sophie,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.12,Default,Tom Borden,0,0,0,,那个 我们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:50.32,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,我们有「马」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:00.55,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,由希奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:04.62,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,请用这个跟黑部保持联络
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:09.70,Default,Sebastian,0,0,0,,因为无法在神器上增设我们通讯装置
