Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,剑酱好帅呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.42,Default,Kennosuke,0,0,0,,出发了
